We are 8 days into the 4th quarter! How are you guys doing? As you are working toward your goals remember: 

1. MONEY MATTERS 
Plan for the soft times and slow sales especially around the holidays. It’s okay to do specials and promotions for quick income. Consumers will always appreciate a “good bang for a buck!”

2. IMPROVE YOUR MARKETING 
Consumers are visual, make them feel like they need and want what you’re selling, put them there mentally and it’s sold! 

3.LOOK BACK & FORWARD 
Evaluate what you would want to change about how your business operated this year. We are working smart not hard! Entrepreneurs can’t have fried brains, we can’t stay creative and innovative. 

4. SET MICRO GOALS 
You can do a lot in 12 weeks, set small 1-2 goals per week to get to the bigger goal, but remember to stay realistic.
